	* tests/local.at (AT_CHECK_AUTOM4TE): Fix typo in the comment.

2005-12-02  Paul Eggert  <eggert@cs.ucla.edu>

	* doc/autoconf.texi (Limitations of Builtins): Fix typos in previous
	patch, noted by Ralf Wildenhues.

