	* lib/autotest/general.m4 (_AT_DECIDE_TRACEABLE): New macro.
	(_AT_CHECK): Use it.
	* lib/m4sugar/m4sh.m4 (AS_ESCAPE_FOR_EXPAND): Remove.
	(AS_ESCAPE): Fix comment.
