	* lib/m4sugar/m4sh.m4 (_AS_TR_SH_PREPARE, _AS_TR_CPP_PREPARE):
	Use 'eval', so that the resulting configure scripts work even if
	the current directory has a weird file name like 'y%s+%pp%;s%@%_%g'.

