	Update from masters.

2002-05-29  Paul Eggert  <eggert@twinsun.com>

	* bin/autom4te.in ($m4): Do not assume that egrep and fgrep exist.
	* lib/autoconf/c.m4 (AC_C_BIGENDIAN): Likewise.
	* lib/autoconf/general.m4 (_AC_RUN_LOG_STDERR, AC_EGREP_CPP):
	Likewise.
