2002-01-17  Jim Meyering  <meyering@lucent.com>

	* lib/autoconf/lang.m4 (_AC_COMPILER_EXEEXT_DEFAULT): Initialize
	$ac_cv_exeext so we don't use an old, invalid, cached value.

