	* lib/autoconf/general.m4 (_AC_INIT_PREPARE): We cleaning up the
	trailing files, don't apply `-rf' to files which might not be
	created by configure (core, core.*, and *.core), but just `rm -f'.
	Suggested by Jonathan Kamens.

