	Reported by Michael Elizabeth Chastain.

	* autoconf.in: Refuse such AWK.
	* configure.in: Likewise.
	* Makefile.am (acversion.m4): Do not use move-if-change this file
	has dependencies.
	* doc/autoconf.texi (Fortran 77 Compiler): Some typos.

